A parametrized curve $$\gamma$$ is a //geodesic,// if for all of its variations $$\gamma(x,t)$$ with compact support we have

$$
\dot L \coloneqq \fracpartial{}{t} \biggr|_{t=0}\, \int_0^L \d s = 0.
$$